{"type": "article", "id": 22870, "title": "在冬日的森林里，住一晚温暖的山间木屋", "description": "它触及到森林里，但对环境产生较小干预。", "date": "2016-02-26T07:00:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1225, "name": "美国"}, {"id": 19098, "name": "木屋"}, {"id": 23998, "name": "HGA"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702114419VOq0itMmHhxsveU6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>距离美国明尼苏达州 Minneapolis（明尼阿波利斯）48 公里的 Whitetail 森林公园里，有 3 间小木屋可以对外出租。它们拥有普通小木屋的所具有的特征，斜坡屋顶以及方盒子一样的形状，不同的只是带有黑色木纹的表面，像瓦片一样层层覆盖在上面，在周围深色树干的遮挡下，像是真的隐藏在森林里。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114410wo1MSnJjIb8K67Ua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114411EYl3UD6qMnkgsFx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114412KyeCzFViHxp6NkSn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114412gO1S3CriEQMJeAqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.21474359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">木屋的主体用了棕红色的雪松木，有深浅相间的纹路。依靠混凝土的支撑站立在斜坡上，需要通过一小段连接的桥才能进入室内。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021144135zVh9xW6NFL2rBOU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114413rAHkifJWY6hUXQZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114414C7P9W1dBoVkmig68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>走进室内，棕红色的雪松木完全包裹了小房间，搭配橙黄色的灯光，令人感到格外的温暖。室内其实只有 21㎡，但并不显得拥挤。两张上下床靠着一头的墙边，剩下地方有沙发和餐桌，给公共区域留出了较大的空间。床铺可以住 4 个人，但 2 张沙发可供格外 2 个人睡。这附近有一处公共的浴室以供使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114414UJ892ygSWF3Gv6DM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114415n9lmAaLeYFBKjvq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114416UzVapMCwG2mTvE7R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.38888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>木屋的旁边有滑雪和登山的走道，它恰好在半山腰，也为人们提供了一个休息的地方。修建者 HGA （Hammel, Green and Abrahamson）规划了这些木屋和一些艺术雕塑，他们希望公众更多地来这里。租借一晚需要大约 $60，也是一个可接受的价格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114416zRWe2cOgo7HkuPBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52678571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114417vCaXAImeR6tO7Tsj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66964286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://hga.com/work/dakota-county\">HGA</a> 是明尼阿波利斯当地一家老牌建筑事务所，成立于 1953 年。修建这所木屋得到了许多学生的帮助。它最近获得了一个由木制产品委员会颁发的 Wood Design Awards ，源于它触及到森林里，但对环境产生较小干预。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114417RaWklvunExp2SdQB.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7542735\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114418tG5OWdFr1CZm9XuD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84935897\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021144187qhzuW8nxZNUXLHG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.355\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/02/23/hga-architects-engineers-cedar-cabins-forested-hillside-minnesota-usa/\">dezeen</a>、<a href=\"https://hga.com/work/dakota-county\">hga</a></p>\n\n\n"}